## Adidas Shoes Landing Page

Here's a design concept and the HTML & CSS code for an Adidas shoes landing page, incorporating their branding:

**Design Concept:**

* **Hero Section:** Large background image showcasing a popular Adidas shoe model. Bold headline highlighting a current promotion or new release. Clear call-to-action button.
* **Featured Shoes Section:** Grid display of 3-4 featured Adidas shoe models, each with a small image, title, and price.
* **Technology Section:** Showcase key Adidas shoe technologies (e.g., Boost, PrimeKnit) with icons and brief descriptions.
* **Testimonial Section:** Include a customer testimonial with a photo and quote highlighting the quality and comfort of Adidas shoes.
* **Footer:** Standard footer with Adidas logo, copyright, and links to social media.

**Color Palette:** Black, white, and Adidas signature blue (#1e447a).

**Typography:** Adidas uses a custom typeface, but for this example, we'll use a similar sans-serif font like Roboto.

**HTML (index.html):**

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Adidas Shoes</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="style.css">
</head>
<body>

    <header class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>Find Your Perfect Stride</h1>
            <p>Explore the latest Adidas shoe innovations for peak performance and style.</p>
            <button class="btn">Shop Now</button>
        </div>
    </header>

    <section class="featured-shoes">
        <h2>Featured Shoes</h2>
        <div class="shoe-grid">
            <div class="shoe">
                <img src="shoe1.jpg" alt="Adidas Shoe 1">
                <h3>Ultraboost 22</h3>
                <p>$180</p>
            </div>
            <div class="shoe">
                <img src="shoe2.jpg" alt="Adidas Shoe 2">
                <h3>Stan Smith</h3>
                <p>$85</p>
            </div>
            <div class="shoe">
                <img src="shoe3.jpg" alt="Adidas Shoe 3">
                <h3>Superstar</h3>
                <p>$90</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="technology">
        <h2>Innovative Technology</h2>
        <div class="tech-grid">
            <div class="tech">
                <img src="boost.png" alt="Boost Technology">
                <h3>Boost</h3>
                <p>Unmatched energy return for a responsive and comfortable ride.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="tech">
                <img src="primeknit.png" alt="PrimeKnit Technology">
                <h3>PrimeKnit</h3>
                <p>Adaptive fit and lightweight comfort for a sock-like feel.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="testimonial">
        <div class="testimonial-content">
            <img src="testimonial.jpg" alt="Customer Testimonial">
            <p>"These Adidas shoes are the most comfortable I've ever owned! The Boost technology is amazing." - John S.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <footer>
        <img src="adidas-logo.png" alt="Adidas Logo">
        <p>&copy; 2023 Adidas. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>

</body>
</html>
```

